data.meta_description: The I Love CVille Show with Jerry Miller spotlights The Best of Charlottesville, Virginia! The I Love CVille Show streams live to Facebook Monday through Friday from 12:30 pm - 1:30 pm. You can also catch the archived version of each episode on iLoveCVille.com.
